import React from 'react'
import ReactDom from 'react-dom'
import Uppericons from './uppericons'
import Lowericons from './lowericons'
const MainLayout = () => {
    return (


        <div className = "main-layout" >
     
        <
        div class = "row" >
        <
        div class = "col-sm-2" >
        <
        Uppericons / >
        <
        /div>

        <
        div class = "col-sm-8" >


     <
        /div> <
        div class = "col-sm-2" >
        <
        Lowericons / >
        <
        /div>

        <
        /div>



        <
        /div>


    );
}

export default MainLayout;
